This one is stable, almost unbannable, and uses free resources accessable from anywhere
Shout to karlee hawkins for creating the orignal code for this to work :)

1. go to https://replit.com/@KarleeHawkins/StudyTime-3 
2. press run and profit (wait for it to load because it's a lot less optimized)

OPTIONAL (for better viewing of the virtual browser)
3. create an account
4. fork the repository
5. run the code as normal and change the window size to the maximum it can be
6. profit in a larger window ez
